            <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>

            <p>We may update these terms from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates the most recent revision. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.</p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>

            <p>Questions about these terms can be directed to us through our GitHub repository at <a href="https://github.com/poolboy17/digging-scriptures" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">github.com/poolboy17/digging-scriptures</a>.</p>

        </article>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
